articles.title: Gazi Fanart Using Figma
articles.rawContent:
![Gazi Pathseeker](/img/posts/vector-art/gazi.svg)

Featuring [Gazi Pathseeker](https://thewanderinginn.fandom.com/wiki/Gazi_Pathseeker) from [The Wandering Inn](https://wanderinginn.com/).

Made in [Figma](https://figma.com/). See interactive version at [The Wandering Inndex](https://inndex.omg.lol/gazi).
